sources.description:
TRAPPED by a bullet blockade! 
Cowboys Shamrock (Jimmy "Shamrock" Ellison) and Lucky (Russ "Lucky" Hayden) ride into a range war and end it.

Original B&W version: https://youtu.be/Buy6j9l9xB4
aka Outlaw Fury
Director: Thomas Carr
Writers: Ron Ormond, Maurice Tombragel, Forbes Parkhill
Stars: James Ellison, Russell Hayden, Raymond Hatton, Fuzzy Knight, Julie Adams, Tom Tyler
Genre: Classics, Western
